nment/bengali/movie-details/antare-bahire/movieshow/62525740.cms|website=www.timesofindia.indiatimes.com|access-date=2019-07-07}}</ref> Arindam Bhattacharjee is the cinematographer of the film.<ref name=":0" /> The film stars [[Debashree Roy]] and [[Abhishek Chatterjee]],<ref name="Cast of the film">{{cite web|title=Cast of the film |url=http://www.antorebahire.com/about/cast/ |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130117071137/http://www.antorebahire.com/about/cast/ |url-status=dead |archive-date=17 January 2013 |accessdate=14 December 2012 }}</ref> and marks the big screen debut of actress Chitrangada Chakraborty.<ref name="CC" /> The music and background score of the film was composed by Chandan Roy Chowdhury with lyrics penned by Somnath Sen.<ref name=":0" />
== Synopsis == Dipto and Riddhi are married working in a corporate office, both have busy work schedules. All was well until Dipto began an extra maritial affair with his colleague, Shruti. Presently, they are awaiting a divorce. A mysterious entity known as Khushi enters their lives and controls their destinies.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.zee5.com/movies/details/antore-bahire/0-0-9902|title=Antore Bahire (2012)|website=www.zee5.com|access-date=2019-07-07}}</ref>
